latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Mother Earth
Let’s save our planet together!

Day after day , she provides 
the air we breathe , the food we eat, the ground beneath our feet.
She treats us to sun bright skies,
And marvels like mountains,
Forests, oceans and streams,
Singing birds and swaying trees. 

Let’s all pledge to protect at least 1 tree in our neighbourhood as a gift to our Mother Earth on this Mother’s Day!

@theterracoindia

Rupali said, “ Main iss desh ki beti hu aur iss desh ne mujhe boht kuch dia hai – iss desh ki mitti, kheton ke rang, Charkha, anekta mei ekta, haldi ki khushboo, shiksha , aage badhne ka saahas, rangon se bhara mera Bharat.

Writing a letter to the one you spent your childhood fighting and loving. Growing up to this day on our path of life and with those little memories. 
This Rakshabandhan write a letter to your brother not just a Rakhi but an emotion.
